  "instructions": [
    "Heat olive oil in a wok or large skillet over medium heat.",
    "Add minced garlic, cumin seeds, and red chili flakes; saut\u00e9 for about 1 minute.",
    "Stir in frozen peas. Pour tomato paste over the mixture and mix well to coat all peas evenly.",
    "Cook until most of the water has evaporated from the peas, about 5 minutes. Add chopped coriander leaves and cook for another 2-3 minutes or until you reach desired consistency.",
    "Serve hot as a side dish with your favorite meals."
